General.Name: Chenghe Acquisition Co. Warrant
General.Description: Chenghe Acquisition Co. focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to identify business opportunities in the field of financial technology or technology-enabled financial service companies, including artificial intelligence, big data, and cloud and blockchain-related initiatives in Asian markets. The company was founded in 2021 and is based in Singapore.
